{"lemma":"جَمَراتٌ","slug":"جَمَراتٌ","root":"ج.م.ر","root_slug":"ج-م-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/ج-م-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":5},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n6267","n6272"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AC%D9%8E%D9%85%D9%8E%D8%B1%D8%A7%D8%AA%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"ember, cinder, live coal","tags":["collective"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be covered by heat, to convene into a focal point (as by being close to the sun, or blushing, or in a people’s assembly …)"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to collect together, to unite"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to cense, to fumigate"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to roast"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n6267","headword_ar":"جمّر","root":"jmr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tajomiyrN","text_ar":"تَجْمِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamara","text_ar":"جَمَرَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Msb;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He collected together"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, K) a people, and anything. (Msb.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jam~arato $aEarahaA","text_ar":"جَمَّرَتْ شَعَرَهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tajomiyrN","text_ar":"تَجْمِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, A, K;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamaratohu","text_ar":"جَمَرَتْهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ajomaratohu","text_ar":"اَجْمَرَتْهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"She"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a woman)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"collected together her hair,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and tied it in knots,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made it knotted and crisp,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eaqadatohu","text_ar":"عَقَدَتْهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", S, A, Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"at the back of her neck;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, Msb, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not letting it hang down loosely:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"plaited it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, TA:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jm~r $aEarahu","text_ar":"جمّر شَعَرَهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he collected together his hair at the back of his head:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raA^osahaA","text_ar":"رَاْسَهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ajmrt","text_ar":"اجمرت","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"she collected together the hair of her head, and plaited it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aEarahu","text_ar":"شَعَرَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ajmr","text_ar":"اجمر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he disposed his hair in"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*awaAy^ib","text_ar":"ذَوَايِب"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"locks hanging down loosely from the middle of the head to the back,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"plaits hanging down"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jm~r","text_ar":"جمّر"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a thing)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"necessitated a people to unite together."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b4-  Also, (inf. n. as above, S,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a commander, As, A)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"detained"},{"kind":"text","text":"the army"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the territory of the enemy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"on the frontier of the enemy's country,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and did not bring"},{"kind":"text","text":"them"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"back"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from the frontier:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) the doing of which is forbidden: (TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he detained"},{"kind":"text","text":"them"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"long on the frontier of the enemy, and did not give"},{"kind":"text","text":"them"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"permission to return to their families:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(As, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he collected"},{"kind":"text","text":"them"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"on the frontiers of the enemy, and kept"},{"kind":"text","text":"them"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from returning to their families."},{"kind":"page_break","n":453},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A2-  See also 4: ―         -b2-  and 5.       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jm~r Alv~awoba","text_ar":"جمّر الثَّوْبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A, Mgh, Msb,) inf. n. as above, (Mgh, Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He fumigated the garment with perfume;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, * Mgh, Msb;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ajmrhu","text_ar":"اجمرهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Mgh, Msb, K:) but the former is the more common. (Mgh.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jm~r Almasojida","text_ar":"جمّر المَسْجِدَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Mgh, TA,) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ajmrhu","text_ar":"اجمرهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", accord. to different modes of writing the surname of a certain No'eym, i. e.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Almujam~iru","text_ar":"المُجَمِّرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Almujomiru","text_ar":"المُجْمِرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) [and accord. to different copies of the K,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He fumigated the mosque with perfume:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh:) [or perhaps it may mean"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he strewed the ground of the mosque with pebbles;"},{"kind":"text","text":"from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamorapN","text_ar":"جَمْرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaS~abahu","text_ar":"حَصَّبَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaSabapN","text_ar":"حَصَبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaSobaA='u","text_ar":"حَصْبَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaSobapN","text_ar":"حَصْبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jm~r","text_ar":"جمّر"},{"kind":"text","text":"[for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jm~r laHomFA","text_ar":"جمّر لَحْمًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He put flesh-meat upon live coals"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to roast"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.)       -A4-  Also, (A,) inf. n. as above, (S, A,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a pilgrim, A)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"threw the pebbles"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in the valley of Minè]; (S;) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Astjmr","text_ar":"استجمر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tw","text_ar":"تو"},{"kind":"text","text":".) Hence,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yawomu Alt~ajomiyr","text_ar":"يَوْمُ التَّجْمِير"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The day of the throwing of the pebbles,"},{"kind":"text","text":"by the pilgrims, in the valley of Minè]. (A.) [See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamorapN","text_ar":"جَمْرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]       -A5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jm~r Aln~axolapa","text_ar":"جمّر النَّخْلَةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (inf. n. as above, A,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He cut off the heart,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pith,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jum~aAr","text_ar":"جُمَّار"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the palmtree."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A. K. *)"}],"source_refs":["Msb","K","S","A","T","TA","Mgh","As"]},{"entry_id":"n6272","headword_ar":"جَمْرٌ","root":"jmr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see what next follows, in two places."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}